          (v.adicCompletionIntegers ℚ).subtype.toIntLinearMap).toAddMonoidHom).range)]) ≃ₜ+
    (V ⊗[ℚ] InfiniteAdeleRing ℚ) ×
    (Πʳ v : IsDedekindDomain.HeightOneSpectrum (𝓞 ℚ),
